data.title: Yes, Prime Minister Cast Members List
data.meta_description: List of actors and actresses who star in Yes, Prime Minister (list of Yes, Prime Minister cast members).
data.text:
Paul Clark Eddington, CBE (18 June 1927 – 4 November 1995) was an English actor who appeared in the television sitcoms The Good Life and Yes Minister/Yes Prime Minister. more »

Derek Fowlds (2 September 1937 – 17 January 2020) was an English actor, best known for playing Bernard Woolley in the British television comedies Yes Minister and Yes Prime Minister, and Oscar Blaketon in the long-running ITV police drama Heartbeat, a ... more »

Sir Nigel Barnard Hawthorne CBE (5 April 1929 – 26 December 2001) was an English actor. He portrayed Sir Humphrey Appleby, the Permanent Secretary in the 1980s sitcom Yes Minister and the Cabinet Secretary in its sequel, Yes, Prime Minister. For this ... more »

Francis George Middlemass (28 May 1919 – 8 September 2006) was an English actor, who even in his early career played older roles. He is best remembered for his television roles as Rocky Hardcastle in As Time Goes By, Algy Herries in To Serve Them ... more »

Diana Hoddinott (born 1945) is an English actress. She is best known for playing Annie Hacker, the wife of Jim Hacker, in the television comedy serials Yes Minister and Yes, Prime Minister. She also had a role in the historical film, The Gathering Storm ... more »

John Nettleton (5 February 1929 – July 2023) was an English actor best known for playing Sir Arnold Robinson, Cabinet Secretary in Yes Minister (1980–1984) and President of the Campaign for Freedom of Information in the follow-up Yes, Prime Minister ... more »
